data.description: Discover serenity and space in this stunning 3 bed, 3 bath ranch home boasting 3560 sf and a 3-car Attached Garage on over a quarter acre lot w/ a finished lower level. Natural light floods the open-concept living room, accentuated by the vaulted ceiling & w/b fireplace. Entertain in the spacious kitchen, complete w/ 42 in cabinets, Corian countertops, all new stainless appliances & ample counter space. Retreat to the luxurious master suite, featuring jetted tub, dbl vanities, sep. shower, bidet & walk-in closet. One additional bedroom, full hall bath, sun rm & laundry rm round out the main level. The finished LL provides even more room to relax or entertain, with large rec room w/ bar, bedroom, & bonus rm for a media room, game room, office, add'l sleeping quarters, in-law suite, or fitness area, cedar closet & full bath. Enjoy the fenced, landscaped yard w/ covered deck & patios to enjoy the outdoors year-round. Updates include: furnace (2023), HWH (2019), laminate flooring (2004).
